{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications."}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"setLanguage:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setLanguage:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"language","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The language code (e.g., “en”, “de”, “fr”, “es”) or nil to reset to device language","type":"text"}]}],"name":"language"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Override the device language for Pushwoosh to enable:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Sending notifications in a specific language","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Language-based segmentation","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Supporting in-app language switching","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a lowercase two-letter code according to ISO-639-1 standard."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Support in-app language selection:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LanguageManager {","","    static let shared = LanguageManager()","","    var currentLanguage: String {","        didSet {","            applyLanguageChange()","        }","    }","","    func applyLanguageChange() {","        \/\/ Update Pushwoosh language for targeted notifications","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","","        \/\/ Update user tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"language\": currentLanguage,","            \"language_changed_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Update app UI","        Bundle.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","        NotificationCenter.default.post(name: .languageDidChange, object: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"App language changed to: \\(currentLanguage)\")","    }","","    func resetToDeviceLanguage() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(nil)","        currentLanguage = Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“zh” (Chinese), “ja” (Japanese), “ko” (Korean), “ru” (Russian)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setLanguage:"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":